author: Kevin Green | Progress Sports Editor
title: GIRLS WRESTLING: Claremore dominates Inola Invitational, secures team championship
text:
Claremore's girls wrestling team continued its stellar season, claiming the team championship at the Inola Girls Invitational last week with 151.5 points. Inola and Oologah also represented Rogers County well, finishing second and fourth, respectively.
With multiple individual champions and strong finishes, the Lady Zebras showcased their depth and skill throughout the tournament.
